1. INTRODUCTION
Terminal racing is simple horse racing simulation for Linux terminal.

2. INSTALLATION
Clone repositiory or download and unpack zip.

3. RUN
Run ./terminalRacing.sh or ./terminalRacing [track size] [track lenght]

